    if(this.country.equals(cmp.getCountry())){
        return false;
    }

    if(this.regCode == null || this.regCode.equals(cmp.getCode())){
        return false;
    }

You&#39;re missing the `!` (NOT) operator:

    if (! this.country.equals(cmp.getCountry())) {
        return false;
    }

    if (this.regCode == null || ! this.regCode.equals(cmp.getCode())) {
        return false;
    }

Also, your `hashCode()` implementation implies that `country` can be `null`, so you&#39;re missing the null-check:

    if (this.country == null || ! this.country.equals(cmp.getCountry())) {
        return false;
